059200
059300     IF      COMS-IN-STATUS          =       0 OR 92 OR 93
059400             NEXT    SENTENCE
059500     ELSE
059600     IF      COMS-IN-STATUS          =       99
059700             GO                      TO      020-S-PROCESSA
059800     ELSE
