061500
061600
061700     ACCEPT  AX-TIME                 FROM    TIME.
061800
061900
062000     MOVE    "N"                     TO      CH-RECRIA-NPL.
062050     MOVE    "N"                     TO      CH-GRAVA-TAXAS4.
062100
062200     IF      IN-CODE                 =       "V140"
062300             PERFORM 030-E-TRNS      THRU    030-S-TRNS
062400     ELSE
062500             MOVE    999             TO      IA1
062550             MOVE    033             TO      AX-LENGTH
062600             PERFORM 140-E-MSGOUT    THRU    140-S-MSGOUT.
062700
062800
062900
063000
